body:multipart-form {
  content: '''
    Two of my Apify actors were quietly broken and I didn't notice 👀
    
    Market Gap Analyzer: runaway token usage on bad inputs
    Fake Applicant Detector: silently failing health checks - root cause was Gemini being rate limited
    
    Fixed both + refactored all 6 actors to use Gemini model rotation
    Rate limit on one → auto-fallback to the next. No downtime, no manual intervention.
    
    Spent the later part of my holiday doing infra work. 0 regrets.
    
    Building resilient > building new
    
    #BuildInPublic #Apify #IndieHacker #AIAgents #LLM #SideProject
  '''
  platforms: X
  scheduled_time: 2026-03-04T02:00:00.000Z
  ~media: 
}

